subject: Rhythmic Gymnastics
Olympic Games (2008)
lead_paragraph: When the rhythmic gymnast Lisa Wang took the gold at the Pan American Games in July, she thought she would be heading to China in 2008. But four months later, she has not qualified to compete in Beijing.
